    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Urllib3 Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Urllib3</application> module is a powerful, user-friendly
HTTP client for Python. It brings many critical features that are missing
from the Python standard libraries.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

